{"tid":1440882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「打遊擊」去最多人，特別遊客多嘅點","createTime":"2019-08-10T14:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:07:11.000Z","uid":296350,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f534287809719cbe6a19fb68aa175ed1cf479ef3","tid":1440882,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:11:04.000Z","msg":"打遊擊遍地開花，去最多人同遊客嘅點<br />\n狗一出嚟部防，就轉場！！<br />\n<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">引發現場市民參與</span></strong></span></span></strong>， 比市民親身見證黑狗嘅癲狂， 令原本冇主動參與嘅人都置身其中，可能下次佢哋就會一齊出嚟<br />\n<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">可做掩護比手足轉場</span></strong>， 不受傷，不被捕， 玩多幾個場<br />\n雖然咁樣前線好辛苦， 總好過要流血同要坐。<br />\n<br />\n3. <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">撚狗撚到出神入化</span></strong>， 鳩企，鳩衝空氣，鳩屌空氣， 鳩對空氣放 彈，唔使好耐 ，佢哋有人會撳自動引爆器<br />\n<br />\n4. <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">連輿論同民心都贏埋</span></strong>，畀全世界睇住佢哋亂鳩咁做<br />\n<br />\n5.<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">令更多人支持我哋， 仲開埋國際線</span></strong>，向冇參與嘅普通市民（ 包括遊客）放催淚彈或推進， 佢哋傷及無辜<br />\n<br />\n做到以上幾點，手足無須戀戰， 既安全又有效！<br />\n唔使衝，唔使掉磚，唔使放火， 要有足夠體力，要跑得快可轉場！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">狗嘅IQ同EQ都比人低</span></strong>，佢哋越嬲就越會做錯，好撚嬲又冇人畀佢打，唯有自焚！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">等睇幾時有狗吞槍或跳樓</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f49eb41a6335fae1705c4706cc5f1aed01b07e41","tid":1440882,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:13:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aacf1380b5dcaeaab51c04a770c314c351b736dc","tid":1440882,"uid":185960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:14:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=ac552a42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n[文宣］黑白大字報 政權罪行 遍地開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360258</a><br />\n<br />\n文宣就係做比藍絲、港豬<br />\n做比自己人睇有撚用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75be9855181474da6ff749194d7cf7cc87edfa1f","tid":1440882,"uid":296350,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"不停聽到記者報導<br />\n唔知點解放催淚彈<br />\n唔知個目標係咩<br />\n前面冇人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c56c11abe9728ac63958521505328ebee14aad","tid":1440882,"uid":296350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:20:45.000Z","msg":"大圍記者話<br />\n一隊防暴警察<br />\n突然快速向前推進<br />\n但係前面冇示威者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f457013c5d17d3767d6ac22e98ee8a49c55e07","tid":1440882,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:24:04.000Z","msg":"目標唔止係撚狗，要引更多人關注同支持<br />\n<br />\n槍頭依然對住政權同政制"},{"pid":"b699d0e3e42a1d224ce049e3f81e011fe87b72e2","tid":1440882,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:33:37.000Z","msg":"槍頭對準政權同政制！！<br />\n<br />\n狗係condom<br />\n只係畀我哋攞分同攞籌碼<br />\n<br />\n令黑警犯錯，令佢哋自焚 <br />\n已經達到目標效果"},{"pid":"a302857e0f9ecbaa7f68a9d1bf8f0c08a72b7a95","tid":1440882,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:40:37.000Z","msg":"遍地開花唔止街頭抗爭 <br />\n仲有其他戰線一齊做"},{"pid":"f0bd1a58ffc8ea8ebfe5ccb8284587aa8854c9c8","