IHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"765d0e1f22d3f52e7d01ec2f27f29ddca416fb29","tid":1440882,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:36:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3ec6e87bdd72187157c97bd6e7bab350cd56b43","tid":1440882,"uid":164477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b597440da6d9700f896b0d6dc0fb4b3ce9e71047","tid":1440882,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:58:12.000Z","msg":"重新整理<br />\n記者可唔可以有共識！！<br />\n呢啲係我哋最關心嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n<strong>每日無論邊個問先，頭幾條都要係呢幾條！！<br />\n每一次問都數， 呢條問題係第幾次第幾日問，未有答案！ 幾時先會有答案？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">請準備好每條問題嘅影片及圖片</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 721點解唔執法？點解只告非法集會？點解全部未落charge？<br />\n播圖播片<br />\n指揮官喺村公所同白衣人對話，當時佢哋手持武器， 點解唔執法？<br />\n播片<br />\n<br />\n2 有證據顯示警方用過期Tear Gas?用咗幾多?點解用?<br />\n請準備圖及片<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n過期催淚彈 成分變質變山埃， 警方會否道歉及賠償？<br />\n<br />\n3. 警察係咪扮示威者，然後執法？ 點解用咁嘅策略 ？有冇掉磚？有冇煽動？有冇放火？會否Charge佢哋參與暴動?<br />\n準備圖及片<br />\n<br />\n4. 點解會係地鐵站 內放催淚彈同胡椒彈？目的係驅趕定拘捕？<br />\n準備片<br />\nFollow up questions<br />\n如果係驅趕，佢哋已經喺地鐵站走緊！ 點解仲要放？ 如果係拘捕，你應該衝入去拉人而唔係放催淚彈胡椒彈！可唔可以解釋下<br />\n<strong>預設答案：</strong>情況混亂，個別事件<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n警察冇專業訓練處理混亂情況？<br />\n個別例子係合理解釋？殺人放火強姦都係個別例子！ 示威者都係混亂情況下先做出唔尋常，唔理智行為，警方接唔接受呢個解釋唔落charge？<br />\n<br />\n5. 有片影到警察放武器入示威者背囊，點解？係唔係插贓嫁禍？<br />\n<strong>預設答案&nbsp;：</strong>&nbsp;冇資料<br />\n預備嗰條片， 講埋時間地點<br />\n叫佢解釋！<br />\n<br />\n6. 太古零距離開槍， 做法是否恰當？咩原因同情況下要咁做？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n7. 北角警察無視白衣人攻擊黑衣人及記者， 荃灣白衣人 一離場，場警察就進場，又係一個巧合？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n一齊畀意見！！<br />\n葵芳地鐵站內放催淚彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchishing87%2Fvideos%2F10156292523426674%2F&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=63faec4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/</a><br />\n<br />\n追打並推落扶手電梯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2196364073824126&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=5e53b3fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126</a><br />\n<br />\n太古站開槍 1米內射示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424996360930416&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=c39adaa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416</a><br />\n<br />\n竹支嫁禍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424974427599276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424974427599276&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=8d70fb79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424974427599276</a><br />\n<br />\n唔回應是否扮示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196515767142290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2196515767142290&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=1fc9295a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196515767142290</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者會共識<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449180</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8cc7993942456ce49bec039bdb206e8c18a4cd26","tid":1440882,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:07:11.000Z","msg":"不割席，不分化，兄弟爬山<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">個春袋已被敵人楂住咗</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n只要搵幾條仆街帶風就已經成功破解我哋呢三句格言！！<br />\n<br />\n不割不分吖嘛！！<br />\n搵人帶風自然有人跟！！<br />\n搵鬼落場做乜嘢都可以入你數！<br />\n<br />\n再唔諗辦法<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">捉鬼</span></strong>，我哋真係死撚硬！！<br />\n<br />\n要有效捉鬼，前線一定要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">有底線共識</span></strong>，咩可以做，咩唔可以做，一過底線就係鬼，即捉！唔係割席，唔係同分化呀！係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">認真解決問題呀！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n分化同鬼從來都係<strong>狗共致勝之道</strong><br />\n，要對付唯一方法就係<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">團結</span></strong></strong>！！<br />\n既然團結，就嘗試傾個底線共識，唔係所有野要有共識，底線真係有須要呀！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> 手足不割，鬼同分化撚一定要割！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">底線共識大家可以討論</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大前提係畀全世界知我哋係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">為自由良知而戰嘅正義之師，係保護市民嘅黑衣人！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1.可以打遊擊同快閃， 唔放火/唔掉磚/唔衝/唔主動出手/唔傷及無無辜。<br />\n<br />\n2. 可以佔路set路障，圍，口撩，還拖！但不主動出擊，不傷及無辜。<br />\n<br />\n3.不送頭，所有可以被聯上暴動同暴徒嘅，都唔好做。<br />\n<br />\n4. 贏輿論同民心唔係講緊連登呀！自high有乜撚嘢用！<br />\n<br />\n輿論係正常媒體包括 social media 同埋國際輿論，民心唔使講啦！<br />\n<br />\n失民心同輿論，話撚知你連登幾high幾高漲，大家可以返屋企含撚啦！<br />\n<br />\n輿論同民心係要嚟令對家喺國際/同社會有壓力！<br />\n<br />\n只要set到個底線嘅共識， <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋先可以真正團結，<strong><strong></strong></strong>先有機會贏</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁我地先真正做到<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">兄弟爬山 不割席 不分化！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n咁多位手足認真諗諗啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不割席 不分化 兄弟爬山春袋已經畀人對準咗！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1471002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1471002</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}